-# Multi-Currency Wallet System Implementation Plan
-
-## Context
-
-PiggyMetrics lets each income/expense Item carry its own Currency, and the statistics-service normalizes everything to USD for its datapoints, but the account-service has no concept of a wallet. There is no way for a user to see a total balance across all currencies converted into a preferred display currency. This plan adds a multi-currency wallet system to the account-service: per-currency balances, monthly normalization, currency conversion via the statistics-service, REST endpoints, and daily snapshots.
-
----
-
-## Part 1: Statistics-Service (expose exchange rates)
-
-### 1.1 Add `/rates` endpoint to StatisticsController
-**Modify:** `statistics-service/src/main/java/.../statistics/controller/StatisticsController.java`
-- Inject `ExchangeRatesService` (alongside existing `StatisticsService`)
-- Add `GET /rates` method with `@PreAuthorize("#oauth2.hasScope('server')")` returning `Map<Currency, BigDecimal>` from `exchangeRatesService.getCurrentRates()`
-
-### 1.2 Add test for `/rates` endpoint
-**Modify:** `statistics-service/src/test/java/.../statistics/controller/StatisticsControllerTest.java`
-- Add `@Mock ExchangeRatesService exchangeRatesService`
-- Add `shouldGetCurrentRates()` test case
-
----
-
-## Part 2: Account-Service Domain Model
-
-### 2.1 Add month ratios to TimePeriod enum
-**Modify:** `account-service/src/main/java/.../account/domain/TimePeriod.java`
-
-Currently a plain enum. Add a `monthRatio` field so `monthlyAmount = amount * period.getMonthRatio()`:
-- `YEAR(1.0/12.0)`, `QUARTER(1.0/3.0)`, `MONTH(1.0)`, `DAY(30.4368)`, `HOUR(30.4368*24.0)`
-
-### 2.2 Create Wallet domain class
-**New:** `account-service/src/main/java/.../account/domain/Wallet.java`
-
-Fields: `Map<Currency,BigDecimal> balances`, `Map<Currency,BigDecimal> convertedBalances`, `BigDecimal totalBalance`, `BigDecimal totalMonthlyIncome`, `BigDecimal totalMonthlyExpenses`, `BigDecimal netSavingsRatePercent`, `Currency baseCurrency`, `Date lastUpdated`
-
-### 2.3 Create WalletSnapshot + WalletSnapshotId
-**New:** `account-service/src/main/java/.../account/domain/WalletSnapshot.java` - `@Document(collection="wallet_snapshots")` with `@Id WalletSnapshotId id` and `Wallet wallet`
-
-**New:** `account-service/src/main/java/.../account/domain/WalletSnapshotId.java` - compound key with `String account` + `Date date` (mirrors DataPointId pattern from statistics-service)
-
-### 2.4 Add Wallet field to Account
-**Modify:** `account-service/src/main/java/.../account/domain/Account.java`
-- Add `private Wallet wallet` with getter/setter. Existing documents without wallet will deserialize to `null` (no backward compat issue).
